@startuml
!include ../style.puml

participant "Client\n(Txn 1)" as Client
participant "Participant" as Part

note over Client
  Txn Context:
  readTs = 100
end note

'[step]
Client -> Part: TxnWrite(key="X", val="v2")
Part -> Part: writeTs = 105
Part -> Part: intentStore.put("X@105", "v2")
Part --> Client: OK

'[step]
Client -> Part: TxnRead(key="X", readTs=100)
note right of Part
  **Read-Your-Own-Writes**
  Checks intentStore for own txnId FIRST.
  Finds "X@105" (even though 105 > 100).
end note

'[step]
Part --> Client: Return "v2"
@enduml
